assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Chasen Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides logistics, and technical and engineering services in Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Vietnam, the People's Republic of China, and the United States. The company operates through three segments: Specialist Relocation Solutions, Third Party Logistics, and Technical & Engineering. The company's Specialist Relocation Solutions segment offers material handling tools, equipment, and vehicles to relocate machinery and equipment of customers. Its Third Party Logistics segment provides packaging, trucking, distribution, freight forwarding, non- bonded and bonded warehousing, cargo management, and last mile services. The company's Technical & Engineering segment provides design, fabrication, and installation of steel structures, mechanical and electrical installations, including hook-up for production facilities, parts refurbishment, engineering and spares support, facilities management and maintenance, contract manufacturing, process engineering services, 4G and 5G telecommunications, ordnance, solar panel installation, scaffolding equipment and services, and construction activities. Chasen Holdings Limited also offers freight forwarding and shipping, general contracting, artifact packaging, construction and engineering, trucking, relocation, industrial packing, warehousing, rigging, and general building engineering design and consulting services; services on cryogenic pumps; and scaffolding services to construction industries. In addition, the company engages in the general activities related to machinery and equipment; process engineering and construction; structural steel fabrication supply and installation; precision manufacturing of machine tool accessories; and projects and general trading activities. Chasen Holdings Limited was founded in 1995 and is based in Singapore.
